  "body": "![Banner](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/65c1f464b8b07da5d4de8060b4d21595b089fe8b.png)\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">\n  <a title=\"Blueprint\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/blueprint\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Fycyjpbeb&n=-1\" alt=\"Requires Blueprint\"></a>\n  <a title=\"Discord\" href=\"https://discord.gg/6uRtghgWnE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/780149719611473930?color=526557&amp;label=%20&amp;labelColor=54ab6b&amp;logoColor=white&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord\" alt=\"Discord\"></a>\n  <a title=\"Github\" href=\"https://github.com/rosevcook/windswept-delights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Github-Team_Galena?label=&amp;color=c589d0&amp;labelColor=ffa0eb&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=Github&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Github\"></a>\n</p>\n<h3>📖 About:</h3>\n<ul><li>Made by the Creators of Windswept, this mod adds compatibility between Windswept and Farmer’s Delight! You can find Cabinets for Chestnut/Holly/Pine, meat shanks, snow cones, popsicles, cake slices, new bowl foods, and additional cutting and cooking recipes for Windswept items.</li></ul>\n<h3>📖 Requires:</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/windswept\">Windswept</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/farmers-delight\">Farmer's Delight</a></li>\n</ul>",
